    <title>blog使用笔记</title>
    <url>/2022/11/08/blog%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><div id="vBanner_Root">
    <div id="vBanner_Container" style="background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, white ,#66CCFF)">
        <a href="https://vsinger.com/vsinger">
            <div id="vBanner_post" title="Luo Tianyi" style="background-image:url(https://res.vsinger.com/images/258a09a2b0174738840e8b696e86d771.jpg)"></div>
        </a>
        <div id="vLogo_Container">
            
                
                   <div id="vBanner_logo" style="background-image:url(https://dabaizuihei.github.io/bannerImg/luotianyi.png)"></div>     
                    
            
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<blockquote>
<p>嘛，算是一篇笔记吧<br>毕竟有的命令还是不熟悉，在这里就算是记一下<br>然后会随时上来写update</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>


    <div id="aplayer-AratSAIU" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"
         data-id="143952185" data-server="netease" data-type="album" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="true" data-mutex="false" data-listmaxheight="340px" data-preload="none" data-theme="#66CCFF"
    ></div>

<h1 id="从零开始"><a href="#从零开始" class="headerlink" title="从零开始"></a>从零开始</h1><ol>
<li>安装git</li>
<li>配置github地址<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;你的GitHub用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>复制生成的.ssh文件夹里id.rsa.pub中的密钥全部复制</li>
<li>打开Github Settings keys，新建new SSH Key<br>Title自主命名，Key粘贴</li>
<li>安装Node.js</li>
<li>安装Hexo<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
安装完成后初始化<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init blog  #注意这些命令作用在创建的Blog文件夹</span><br><span class="line">hexo n 随便一个页面名字 #创建新页面</span><br><span class="line">hexo g  #生成网页</span><br><span class="line">hexo s  #在本地预览</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
随后打开localhost:4000，本地页面出现</li>
<li>关联Github，打开站点配置文件_config.yml，最下面这样改<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">	type: git</span><br><span class="line">	repo: 这里填入你之前在GitHub上创建仓库的完整路径，记得加上 .git</span><br><span class="line">	branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>安装Git部署插件<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean </span><br><span class="line">hexo g </span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h1 id="更换主题"><a href="#更换主题" class="headerlink" title="更换主题"></a>更换主题</h1><p>一般主题的GitHub页面里都会写，这里是一个实例<br>比如这个主题叫做next</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>打开站点config，把theme后面改成站点名称</p>
<h1 id="图片引用"><a href="#图片引用" class="headerlink" title="图片引用"></a>图片引用</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;/img/图片名称.png&quot;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="B站引用"><a href="#B站引用" class="headerlink" title="B站引用"></a>B站引用</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;iframe width=&quot;100%&quot; height=&quot;576&quot; src=&quot;[播放器链接]&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; frameborder=&quot;no&quot; framespacing=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt; &lt;/iframe&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="网易云引用"><a href="#网易云引用" class="headerlink" title="网易云引用"></a>网易云引用</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% meting &quot;1368967575&quot; &quot;netease&quot; &quot;song&quot; %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="增加ico"><a href="#增加ico" class="headerlink" title="增加ico"></a>增加ico</h1><p><del>路径Hexo\blog\node_modules\hexo-theme-kira\source\lib\iconfont</del><br><del>两个css和js文件，从<a href="http://www.iconfont.cn保存css和js文件后替换/">www.iconfont.cn保存css和js文件后替换</a></del></p>
<h1 id="网站主体路径"><a href="#网站主体路径" class="headerlink" title="网站主体路径"></a>网站主体路径</h1><p><del>Hexo\blog\node_modules\hexo-theme-kira\layout\components</del></p>
<h1 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a>常用命令</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo -g #安装Hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm update hexo -g #升级</span><br><span class="line">hexo init #初始化博客</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>命令简写</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n &quot;我的博客&quot; == hexo new &quot;我的博客&quot; #新建文章</span><br><span class="line">hexo g == hexo generate #生成</span><br><span class="line">hexo s == hexo server #启动服务预览</span><br><span class="line">hexo d == hexo deploy #部署</span><br><span class="line">hexo server #Hexo会监视文件变动并自动更新，无须重启服务器</span><br><span class="line">hexo server -s #静态模式</span><br><span class="line">hexo server -p 5000 #更改端口</span><br><span class="line">hexo server -i 192.168.1.1 #自定义 IP</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean #清除缓存，若是网页正常情况下可以忽略这条命令</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>上传时一般这么写（传不上去多试试）</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>预览</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="常用参数"><a href="#常用参数" class="headerlink" title="常用参数"></a>常用参数</h1><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">参数</th>
<th align="center">默认值</th>
<th align="center">描述</th>
<th align="center">参数位置</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center"><del>cover</del></td>
<td align="center"><del>theme.background.path</del></td>
<td align="center"><del>文章封面</del></td>
<td align="center"><del>Front Matter</del></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center"><del>reprinted</del></td>
<td align="center"><del>false</del></td>
<td align="center"><del>是否为转载文章（转载文章不会标记版权信息）</del></td>
<td align="center"><del>Front Matter</del></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">no_word_count</td>
<td align="center">false</td>
<td align="center">字数统计</td>
<td align="center">Front Matter</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">password</td>
<td align="center">none</td>
<td align="center">文章密码</td>
<td align="center">Front Matter</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h1 id="已安装的插件"><a href="#已安装的插件" class="headerlink" title="已安装的插件"></a>已安装的插件</h1><ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/gitalk/gitalk/blob/master/readme-cn.md">gitalk</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/MIMONATCH/hexo-vtuber-banner">vTuber-Banner</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/lxl80/hexo-admonition">admonition</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/mmdjiji/hexo-bangumis">bangumis</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/HCLonely/hexo-bilibili-bangumi">bilibili-bangumi</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/D0n9X1n/hexo-blog-encrypt/blob/master/ReadMe.zh.md">blog-encrypt</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer/blob/master/docs/README-zh_cn.md">aplayer</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/blob/master/README.zh-CN.md">live2d</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-dplayer">dplayer</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/Z4Tech/hexo-tag-bilibili">tag-bilibili</a></li>
</ul>
<h1 id="外部资料"><a href="#外部资料" class="headerlink" title="外部资料"></a>外部资料</h1><ul>
<li><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs">hexo官方文档</a></li>
<li><a href="https://hexo.kira.host/">Kira Hexo文档</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/Yue-plus/hexo-theme-arknights">Arknights文档</a></li>
